        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Protecting Advice for Small Savers Act of 2017 or the PASS Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill nullifies the Department of Labor's "fiduciary duty" rule (which requires a retirement advisor to act in the best interest of the investor)&nbsp;and otherwise revises standards of conduct for brokers and dealers. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
